orion broadcast <obgi.o> buys ford <f> unit
    denver, june 2 - 
orion broadcast group inc said its majority-owned orion financial
services corp subsidiary has agreed to purchase fn realty services inc
from ford motor co for 1,200,000 to 1,500,000 dlrs in cash and notes.
it said closing is expected within 45 days after receipt of regulatory
approvals. fn provides loan collection, accounting, data processing
and administrative services to the real estate industry. reuter 
